---

<section id="about" class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <p class="text-gold font-medium tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-sm mb-3">July 3, 2026</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">The Countdown Is On</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-red mx-auto"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Two column layout -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Text -->
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <p class="text-red text-sm font-semibold italic text-center md:text-left">
          From inaugural balls to milestone galas, the All-American Ball has brought together leaders, dignitaries, astronauts, world champion athletes, A-list celebrities, members of Congress, and proud Americans for over three decades. The Countdown 250 Ball continues that tradition — elevated to meet a once-in-a-generation moment.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          <strong class="text-navy">America 250</strong> — the 250th anniversary of the United States — is the most anticipated national milestone of our lifetimes. On July 4, 2026, the entire country marks the occasion, and Washington, D.C. will be ground zero for the celebration.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          This historic weekend begins on the evening of July 3! The All-American Countdown 250 Ball is America's formal kickoff to the America 250 weekend. This once-in-a-generation celebration can only take place at the legendary Washington Hilton, the iconic venue that has hosted presidents, world leaders, and the White House Correspondents' Dinner for over 60 years.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          People who experienced the Bicentennial in 1976 still talk about it. This is that moment for our generation. Celebrate in style and pride — live entertainment across 4 stages, 6 grand ballrooms, premium open bars, and a midnight countdown that launches America's 250th birthday.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg font-medium text-navy">
          Be there as history is made.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-xl aspect-[4/3]">
          <img
            src="/images/event/stage-countdown-v2.png"
            alt="Grand stage countdown to America's 250th — 3...2...1... Happy 250!"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover scale-[1.02]"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-32 h-32 bg-navy/10 rounded-lg -z-10"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
